The Bitcoin Module for PrestaShop provides the ability for eCommerce sites using PrestaShop to be able to accept bitcoins for payment.

This open source module integrates with [[BitPay]].

##External Links

* [BitPay payment plugin for PrestaShop](https://github.com/bitpay/prestashop-plugin) project on GitHub

* [BitPay plugins](https://bitpay.com/integrations)

* [Blockchain Receive Bitcoin Payments API V2 PrestaShop Module](http://addons.prestashop.com/en/other-payment-methods/21744-blockchain-receive-bitcoin-payments-api-v2.html) module on addons.prestashop.com


